<template>
    <el-table
      stripe
      style="width: 100%;height: 650px;margin: -20px 0; " 
      :data="tableData">
      <el-table-column
        prop="date"
        label="日期"
        width="120">
      </el-table-column>
      <el-table-column
        prop="name"
        label="文章标题"
        width="120">
      </el-table-column>
      <el-table-column
        prop="writer"
        label="作者"
        width="120">
      </el-table-column>
      <el-table-column
        prop="type"
        label="主题"
        width="120">
      </el-table-column>
      <el-table-column
        prop="content"
        label="简介"
        >
      </el-table-column>
      <el-table-column
      fixed="right"
      label=""
      width="100">
      <template slot-scope="scope">
        <el-button type="success" plain>查看</el-button>
      </template>
    </el-table-column>
    </el-table>
  </template>
  <script>
  export default {
    data() {
      return {
        tableData: [{
          date: '2022-12-25',
          name: '关于如何水报告',
          writer:'小李',
          type:'学习',
          content:'自律自律'
          
        }
    ]
      }
    }
  }
</script>
